{"tid":2046861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"瀝源邨祿泉樓疑初步確診女住客　為防疫拒搭LIFT行樓梯仍中招","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T10:23:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":193,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"fd625d3db7ca22684325d109ce83e54e3834fa10","tid":2046861,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"本港新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情反覆，消息指今晚（1日）再新4宗本地感染的初步確診個案，患者居全部住在瀝源邨祿泉樓，分別7樓、10樓各1名住戶，及8樓2名住戶。晚上10時許，4名患者陸續送往威爾斯親王醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，7樓患者為1名中年婦人，她送院時身穿黑衣運動服，並拖着一個小型行李箱，據悉她為防染疫，平日出入祿泉樓時均「唔敢搭𨋢」，選擇行樓梯，惜卻仍初步染疫。<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎持續16天的零本地感染「斷纜」，昨日（5月31日）錄得2宗本地感染個案，為56歲及34歲夫妻，居住瀝源邨祿泉樓。今日較早時間新增3宗確診個案，為瀝源邨34歲女患者的嘉里物流女同事，分別40歲及36歲女子，曾與她接觸的27歲男救護員為另1名新增個案。"},{"pid":"558b3be485f72d5924eb5af0d781d58d3f130d4b","tid":2046861,"uid":92376,"like":161,"dislike":7,"score":154,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"呢幢樓起碼中三百個<br />\n公屋一幢廿伙 40層樓 有數得計"},{"pid":"da4f4c2303f13fa3ed3553ab512975acb17ed394","tid":2046861,"uid":88743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警就係對面"},{"pid":"9c0332cb8f4de6f651c28ecd8f8a6417cc1fd997","tid":2046861,"uid":27664,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"唔搭Lift啫，但出大廈對門都係要按制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ce7670f5ed9af75f220f8abb5042a92f60cedf","tid":2046861,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c0332cb8f4de6f651c28ecd8f8a6417cc1fd997","tid":2046861,"uid":27664,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"20